name: Insane Balancing on One Leg in Extremely High Places
name_original: Insane Balancing on One Leg in Extremely High Places
description:
Insane Balancing on One Leg in Extremely High Places puts you in control of the adrenaline pumped Mr Insane as he balances insanely with just one leg... in extremely high places.

Maintain your balance with the left and right keys, and jump over oncoming threats with the spacebar, and most importantly... don't fall off!

Originally made for Game Jolt's 3rd Weekend Jam.

Includes Game Jolt highscores.
